Enumeration Type Documentation

enum globus_gram_jobmanager_callout_error_t
 

GRAM Jobmanager Callout Error codes.

Enumeration values:
GLOBUS_GRAM_JOBMANAGER_CALLOUT_BAD_CREDS  Credentials not accepted.
GLOBUS_GRAM_JOBMANAGER_CALLOUT_AUTHZ_SYSTEM_ERROR  Authorization system misconfigured.
GLOBUS_GRAM_JOBMANAGER_CALLOUT_AUTHZ_DENIED  Authorization denied.
GLOBUS_GRAM_JOBMANAGER_CALLOUT_AUTHZ_DENIED_INVALID_JOB  Authorization denied - invalid job id.
GLOBUS_GRAM_JOBMANAGER_CALLOUT_AUTHZ_DENIED_BAD_EXECUTABLE  Authorization denied - executable not allowed.
GLOBUS_GRAM_JOBMANAGER_CALLOUT_ERROR_LAST  Last marker - never used.
